Ok, Tony asked me out, 3 times in one night, HOLY Crap. I never awsered him, so yeah, he's a fag. I would never go out with him. So then, i was looking aroud, for the cutest guys in the place and there were two, Bobby and ****. Bobby is just a friend and i would never go out with him but yeah, that's besides the point.... So,yeah, i was talking to this girl and i said i thought that **** was a total hottie and she said,"Oh, hold on a sec." than she went over and talked to him. She told him that i thought he was a hottie and at this point i'm running to hide, that's how embarsed i was. Well, next thing i know i'm hidding under a table and he's walking over to talk to me. OMG, i this point my heart is beating out of my chest. So, yeah, we meet and it seems he liked me too! I can't believe it... I love him.... it's funny cause, if your a true friend of mine you know that i like Cody still, well, i didn't think of Cody once! And I can't believe it but i actually kissed him, i can't wait to go skateing again next weak, He's really the perfect guy, he's hott, he's smart, he's funny, he's romantic, he's... PERFECT.... I'm never letting him go, oh my god, *Smiles* I have never beed this happy, i will remember this night forever, I'm so writeing him a song, EMM, i'm in love, BIG TIME, HE'S PERFECT!!! Oh and by the way, his name is Mike, *loveing eyes*

*HUGE SMILES*
*KT*

So, do you really want to know what i think, well, post a name of a person and i'll tell you the dead honest truth of what i think about that person. Really, i might not always say what i really think about a person but if you post a name I swear i will tell everylittle detail of what i think about that person and why. SO yeah, today was... uneventful to say the least. Except, my crush has a girlfriend now. Wow, It's 3: 42 and i'm tierd. Emm.... OH DUDE! I was robed! In Choir, i had my walet in my purse and i had a few dollars in my walet and some one stole it. Oh, DANG. I'm so sick of these springfield jerks.... I don't want to date again till highschool! Well, that's cause I'm a strong beilever in true love, and i feel if a person really loves a person but the person has a boyfriend or girlfrined, than that person should wait, if they don't end up together than there not ment to be. Oh my stars, I know some of the funniest, most unaproapriate jokes EVER! No, i'm not going to post them! DId you not notice the unaproapriate part!?! And while we are waiting for me to think of something to write, here are a couple of true facts about BOYZ( I know it's supposed to be a "S" and not a "Z" but I'm speacil like that!):
  
     True fact # 1- boys are like parking spaces, all the good ones are taken!

     True fact # 2- boys are like lava lamps, fun to look at but not very bright.

F.Y.I. I didn't come up with either of these so guys, don't be affended!

Emm.... I can't think of what to write about so once i think of what to write about i'll write about it. DA! 



That's all for now,
still
*KT*

AHH! It's finally here! I got my new Sarah Hudson CD! I know I said that the last entry was my last entry. Well, sadly, i lied. NOW I'M FREAKING OUT Cause lying is a sin. GRR. Darn you caps button!!! Oh my stars, I saw the newish Phantom of the Operea, Oh my stars, i cried, i screamed at random objects, it was fab-u-lous! Gosh, I really miss my dad. You know, I'm getting a little brother soon! I can't wait! I broke up with Owen today. Emm... Oh! I'm so close to being done with my script, i'm on my second to last scene. Emm...yeah, But if you haven't seen the new Phantom of the Operea I urge you to go and see A!S!A!P!. It's the best! You'll cry... and you'll fall in love, and you'll just feel warm, like there is goodness in the world. As far as love, for me, there is actually one guy i like, he's single for today at least. Yeah, so, but I don't have a chance. AHH! I need fake rain right about now! Oh, FyI: When I say fake rain it meens something to hide my real teers. but hay, whatever. I want to start babysitting, there's some classes I'm gonna start takeing to get my babysitting licenes. I LOVE KIDS SO MUCH! When I get older, if i don't become a famous star... i plan on getting in a something so that i can help children who have been abused. I think little midjet are so cute! I started bursting in to tears when i saw my cousin today, the dead one, the one that is in ashes! 

 well, that's it for today, thank you for reading! 

Mark James Coffman Jr. 1987-1997
may he rest in piece
